description:
Good evening and welcome to Nighty Night with Rabia Chaudry: Bedtime Stories To Keep You Awake. Tonight's tale is about a sickness so nasty and contagious, nobody's safe. Please enjoy...Pandemic. 

Tonight's Tale is Written by Travis Madden.
